  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      500.34,
      525.95,
      527.86
    ],
    "text": "Suspect Arrested in Connection with the Rape of a Minor and Another Arrested for Aiding and Abetting the Offence \u2013 Kandy Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0,
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      541.98,
      525.1,
      569.06
    ],
    "text": "The Kandy Police have conducted investigations into the alleged rape of a 15-year-old girl and subsequently arrested the principal suspect on 20 May 2026 in the Bahirawakanda area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      583.65,
      435.7,
      596.93
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 25-year-old monk residing at a temple in Bahirawakanda.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      611.37,
      514.4,
      652.25
    ],
    "text": "During the course of the investigation, a 29-year-old woman from the Bahirawakanda area was also taken into custody on the same day by officers attached to the Kandy Police for allegedly aiding and abetting the commission of the offence.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      666.81,
      513.46,
      707.69
    ],
    "text": "Both suspects were produced before the Kandy Magistrate\u2019s Court on 21 May 2026. The monk was remanded until 01 June 2026, while the female suspect was released on two surety bails of Rs. 200,000 each.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      722.25,
      388.99,
      735.53
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being carried out by the Kandy Police.",
